text: One of the few themes composed by the man Koji Kondo himself, and certainly one of the best. As much as I adored Galaxy and enjoyed 3D World, the fact that Super Mario Odyssey returns to the open world roots of 64 fills me with happiness. Running around tighlty designed sandboxes looking for ways to reach your goal (will there be stars in Odyssey?) always feels like an awesome treasure hunt, and learning these layouts is super satisfying. I'm beyond excited!
